{{Refimprove|date=May 2017}} {{Infobox settlement |name = Namukulu |settlement_type = [[List of villages in Niue|Village]] |image_skyline = |image_alt = |image_caption = |image_map = Namukulu location map.png |mapsize = 250px |map_alt = |map_caption = Namukulu council within Niue |image_map1 = Niue Verwaltungsgliederung.png |mapsize1 = 250px |map_alt1 = |map_caption1 = Administrative map of Niue showing all the villages |coordinates = {{coord|18|57|S|169|54|W|display=inline,title|type:city_source:GNS-enwiki}} |subdivision_type = Country |subdivision_name = {{flag|Niue}} |subdivision_type1 = Tribal Area |subdivision_name1 = [[Motu (tribal area)|Motu]] |leader_title = Assemblyman/MP |leader_name = |leader_title1 = [[Village Council Chairperson]] |leader_name1 = |area_total_km2 = 1.48 |area_sq_mi = |percent_water = |area_magnitude = |elevation_footnotes = |elevation_m = |elevation_ft = |population_footnotes = |population_total = 14 |population_as_of = 2011 |population_density_km2 = 9.46 |population_density_sq_mi= |timezone1 = UTC-11 |utc_offset1 = -11 |area_code = [[Telephone numbers in Oceania|+683]] }} '''Namukulu''' is one of the fourteen [[List of villages in Niue|villages]] of [[Niue]].<ref>{{OSM|r|1558552|Namukulu}}</ref> With a population of 14 (2001 and 2011 census), it is one of the smallest settlements of the island.
